  "texts": [
    "It uses the Requests library to collect the paper titles and first author names from DOIs.",
    "Then it uses PYPDF2 and Regular Expression (RE) libraries to collect each PDF's abstract, introduction, and conclusion.",
    "Then it merges 3 of these sections to get the final model input.",
    "Later it uses the previously trained and saved T5 model to get a summary of each paper.",
    "In the next step, it performs post-processing and merges all summaries to produce a coherent literature review segment."
